      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I should do this to all those fancy certifications and awards I've earned.",
      "zh": "我應該對我所有那些華麗的證書和獎項這樣做。",
      "ja": "これを私が得たすべての華やかな認定証や賞にやるべきだ。",
      "time": "00:03:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I feel like they're bringing customers.",
      "zh": "我覺得它們能帶來顧客。",
      "ja": "それらはお客を呼んでいる気がする。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "People don't care about that stuff.",
      "zh": "人們不在乎那些東西。",
      "ja": "人々はそんなものを気にしない。",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All they care about is what their friends are saying on social media.",
      "zh": "他們只在乎朋友在社交媒體上說什麼。",
      "ja": "彼らが気にするのは友達がSNSで何を言っているかだけだ。",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We should post this.",
      "zh": "我們應該發佈這個。",
      "ja": "これを投稿すべきだ。",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know, I've been thinking maybe we should do a channel.",
      "zh": "你知道，我一直在想，也許我們應該做一個頻道。",
      "ja": "ねえ、チャンネルを作るべきかもと思ってた。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maybe showcase the food.",
      "zh": "也許展示食物。",
      "ja": "食べ物を紹介するかも。",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe we should.",
      "zh": "也許我們應該。",
      "ja": "そうかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But I hate social media.",
      "zh": "但我討厭社交媒體。",
      "ja": "でもSNSは嫌いだ。",
      "time": "00:04:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Besides, I am terrible on camera.",
      "zh": "而且我鏡頭前很糟糕。",
      "ja": "それに、私はカメラの前が苦手だ。",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You would be amazing on camera.",
      "zh": "你在鏡頭前會很棒。",
      "ja": "君はカメラ映えするよ。",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But I'm too tired to argue.",
      "zh": "但我太累了，不想爭論。",
      "ja": "でも議論するには疲れすぎてる。",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "For the moment, I'm going home.",
      "zh": "暫時我先回家了。",
      "ja": "今は帰るよ。",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You got a bed.",
      "zh": "你有床嗎？",
      "ja": "ベッドあるの？",
      "time": "00:04:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "有。",
      "ja": "あるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:39"
    }
  ]
}